# Capability Slice Architecture — Future Vision

**This document describes the target architecture, NOT the current state.**
The current layout uses `portfolio/`, `operations/`, `intelligence/`, `ingestion/`.
This migration has not started.

## Target structure

Each capability becomes a self-contained directory owning its full stack:

```
src/remi/application/
  <capability>/
    SKILL.md          ← cognitive entrypoint for the agent
    references/       ← on-demand docs (IMPL.md, DATA.md)
    scripts/          ← executable code + app.yaml manifests
    assets/           ← templates, schemas, static data
    resolver.py       ← business logic
    views.py          ← read models
    api.py            ← HTTP routes
    cli.py            ← CLI commands
```

